    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i get that there are different views, but isn't it a bit of a false equivalence? like, one side is talking about people literally dying without care, and the other is worried about bureaucracy and markets. surely one of those is more objectively \"correct\" than the other in a modern society?",
